##  🔚 How to run it

From the project folder:

```bash
npm run dev
```

Open the URL it prints (usually `http://localhost:5173`).

When you’re ready to deploy:

```bash
npm run build
```

Then host the `dist/` folder on GitHub Pages / Netlify / Vercel.

